1
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:40,880
You can't die.

2
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:44,120
Don't sacrifice yourself alone.
You still have me.

3
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:46,120
<i>Let me die alone, Taiga.</i>

4
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:48,200
Then you can be with the woman
who loves you.

5
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:50,600
Fire Phoenix is finding a way
to release the pathogen.

6
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,480
Release it at their own event?

7
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:55,800
<i>Goodbye, you foul-mouthed kid.</i>

8
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:57,400
<i>Hope you die happily.</i>

9
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:01,600
Whoa!

10
00:03:02,320 --> 00:03:03,480
Run!

11
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:02,320
Mom.

12
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,320
Who am I really?

13
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,560
I'm your son, right?

14
00:04:06,200 --> 00:04:07,160
Ryu.

15
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,640
What did you find out?

16
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:11,240
I thought you went to work.

17
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:13,760
Yes.

18
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:16,279
I went to work in Thailand.

19
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:18,480
That's where things got unbelievable.

20
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,720
Who did you meet?

21
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,960
They're named Taiga and Indhorn.

22
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:31,800
I heard someone named Khanin

23
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,760
say the three of us are siblings.

24
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:38,760
He wants us to do a DNA test.

25
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:40,320
Khanin?

26
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,960
I always knew that one day,

27
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:47,000
I'd have to tell you this.

28
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:49,680
I wanted to give you more time
to be ready,

29
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:53,760
but I can't keep covering the sky
with my bare hands anymore.

30
00:04:53,840 --> 00:04:54,880
Ryu.

31
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:58,040
Listen to me, son.

32
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:02,760
You're not my biological son.

33
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,040
Ryu.

34
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,120
Ryu.

35
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,760
Ryu.

36
00:05:13,840 --> 00:05:15,840
It's time

37
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:18,960
for you to face the truth.

38
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:22,400
You have siblings.

39
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:26,080
My younger sister is your real mother.

40
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:29,160
Your parents were killed.

41
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:32,640
Khanin risked his life to save you

42
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,320
and bring you here.

43
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:38,640
Your two older brothers
are living in separate places.

44
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:42,000
We had to hide the truth

45
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:45,480
to keep the three of you
as safe as possible.

46
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:48,880
So you could grow up
and find the Fire Phoenix

47
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:52,320
that killed your family.

48
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:59,480
My siblings?

49
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,400
My family?

50
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,120
Fire Phoenix?

51
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:18,040
I'm Ryu Dragon.

52
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:22,560
I'm your son.

53
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,560
Not anyone else's.

54
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:30,440
You raised me.

55
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,920
Only you, Mom.

56
00:06:42,640 --> 00:06:44,760
The truth is cruel, son.

57
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:48,360
You may be hurt, Ryu.

58
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,640
But I'm going to tell you everything,

59
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:54,120
and you have to listen with a clear head.

60
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:59,240
Then you'll have to decide
what to do next.

61
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:33,120
Ryu Dragon is back in Hong Kong.

62
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,440
Taiga is still at the farm.

63
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:38,360
Wait.

64
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:40,560
So they made it.

65
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:48,520
Punlop, pick up!

66
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,720
Ugh.

67
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:06,800
What did you give me?

68
00:08:07,520 --> 00:08:08,720
Well…

69
00:08:09,320 --> 00:08:10,480
Please don't blame me.

70
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:13,960
If I didn't do it, I'd be dead.

71
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,640
Oh, no!

72
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:21,040
Hey! Don't!

73
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,200
Damon.

74
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:27,640
Thanks a lot, Giranun.

75
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,520
All that work I did for you

76
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:32,160
wasn't for nothing.

77
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:36,880
I don't have to wait
to be the key man anymore.

78
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:40,960
Because from now on,

79
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:44,760
I'm Damon.

80
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,640
Indhorn is our son.

81
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:55,800
Taiga knows the truth now.

82
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:02,520
Is this related to the explosion?

83
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:05,120
Did they mean to hurt Indhorn?

84
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,480
No.

85
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:07,600
Not Indhorn.

86
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:10,840
They took their little brother hostage.

87
00:10:16,160 --> 00:10:17,640
I was the one

88
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:21,120
who left him at the front of the farm.

89
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:26,760
Dad.

90
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:36,160
Ever since then,

91
00:10:36,880 --> 00:10:40,320
I never let the workers
talk about his past.

92
00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:43,720
We raised him,

93
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:47,160
and we loved him like one of our own.

94
00:10:49,920 --> 00:10:51,320
So that means

95
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:55,520
I'm not really your real son.

96
00:10:57,560 --> 00:10:59,200
Even if you're not,

97
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:01,800
we love you very much.

98
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:09,280
Listen to me.

99
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:15,960
Nothing will ever destroy
the love between the three of us.

100
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:19,120
You have to believe in our love, okay?

101
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,880
I love you so much.

102
00:11:23,680 --> 00:11:24,520
I love you, Mom.

103
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,040
Dad too.

104
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:09,480
His attitude says
he probably knows the truth.

105
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:14,680
Welcome to the family, little brother.

106
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:16,840
There is no such thing as siblings.

107
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:19,800
From now on, I'll handle my own life.

108
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:21,000
I don't need a hero.

109
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:25,840
I'm not some bait
to prove that stupid sibling thing.

110
00:12:25,920 --> 00:12:28,680
If you can't accept it, then shut up
and go back to Hong Kong.

111
00:12:28,760 --> 00:12:30,800
Hey! That's easy for you to say.

112
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:33,520
Who do you think caused all this pain

113
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,520
and almost got me killed?

114
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:35,600
Ryu.

115
00:12:35,680 --> 00:12:37,000
Taiga's warning you because he cares.

116
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:39,160
Indhorn, you're a good person.

117
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:41,120
But you don't have to be good
all the time.

118
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:43,080
No matter what you say,

119
00:12:43,160 --> 00:12:44,240
I still don't like this guy.

120
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,960
This guy is the problem.

121
00:12:46,480 --> 00:12:48,800
Ryu, Taiga is your brother.

122
00:12:48,880 --> 00:12:49,880
Brother?

123
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:54,320
A brother who brings nothing
but endless bad luck to everyone.

124
00:12:55,040 --> 00:12:57,200
If being siblings means
we all have to die together,

125
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,160
then I'd rather be on my own.

126
00:13:00,400 --> 00:13:01,720
You're still young.

127
00:13:01,800 --> 00:13:03,760
I get that you think
everything revolves around you.

128
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:07,520
The only reason I kept everything hidden
was to keep you

129
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:09,640
and Indhorn alive.

130
00:13:11,640 --> 00:13:13,560
We lost our parents.

131
00:13:13,640 --> 00:13:14,960
We were separated.

132
00:13:15,040 --> 00:13:18,680
The one who ordered our parents killed
is still out there.

133
00:13:18,760 --> 00:13:20,760
You probably wouldn't understand, Ryu,

134
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:25,160
how much it hurts to see the father
who raised you shot dead in front of you.

135
00:13:26,880 --> 00:13:28,960
The people who raised us

136
00:13:29,760 --> 00:13:31,600
must never suffer from Fire Phoenix again.

137
00:13:31,680 --> 00:13:33,400
Stop using pain as an excuse

138
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:35,160
and stop using siblings as an excuse too.

139
00:13:36,760 --> 00:13:38,480
Just tell me about Fire Phoenix,

140
00:13:38,560 --> 00:13:39,960
and I'll handle it myself.

141
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:42,000
Nobody wants to die

142
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:43,800
because of someone else's problem.

143
00:13:57,800 --> 00:13:58,760
Hey! Get down!

144
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:28,160
Who is it?

145
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:31,560
Are they Fire Phoenix?

146
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:34,920
If not them, then who?

147
00:14:37,480 --> 00:14:38,800
They just showed up.

148
00:14:39,760 --> 00:14:41,200
They've been after you.

149
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:43,920
I don't have any enemies. Unlike him.

150
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:44,840
You didn't,

151
00:14:44,920 --> 00:14:46,200
until now.

152
00:14:46,280 --> 00:14:48,600
Hey, stop running your mouth.

153
00:14:48,680 --> 00:14:49,840
They're after you.

154
00:14:49,920 --> 00:14:51,920
I don't have time to fight with a kid.

155
00:14:52,520 --> 00:14:54,560
Indhorn, I have to go back to Bangkok.

156
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:57,920
- Wait.
- Stop following me!

157
00:14:58,640 --> 00:15:01,240
Go back to Hong Kong. Now.

158
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:03,960
Don't order me around.
I can think for myself.

159
00:15:04,680 --> 00:15:06,520
Ryu, calm down.

160
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:07,920
If those guys are Fire Phoenix,

161
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:10,560
then your mom
isn't safe in Hong Kong either.

162
00:15:15,840 --> 00:15:17,080
Mom.

163
00:15:17,160 --> 00:15:19,000
Go back and take care of your mom.

164
00:15:19,720 --> 00:15:21,200
Taiga and I will handle it here.

165
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:27,480
Go back before you lose
the chance to see her again.

166
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:35,600
I'm going ahead.

167
00:15:35,680 --> 00:15:36,840
Take care.

168
00:15:56,080 --> 00:15:59,240
You once said Officer Phumin's
little daughter was dead.

169
00:16:00,120 --> 00:16:01,080
Yes.

170
00:16:01,160 --> 00:16:03,120
What if she's still alive?

171
00:16:03,200 --> 00:16:04,280
Why?

172
00:16:05,720 --> 00:16:07,560
Did you find something
on Phumin's hard drive?

173
00:16:08,760 --> 00:16:09,600
No.

174
00:16:10,120 --> 00:16:11,600
Naruban told me himself.

175
00:16:13,360 --> 00:16:17,240
Inspector Phumin's youngest daughter
kept all her father's data,

176
00:16:17,880 --> 00:16:18,760
waiting for revenge.

177
00:16:18,840 --> 00:16:20,440
Impossible!

178
00:16:20,520 --> 00:16:22,720
Only Rin can give us the answer,

179
00:16:23,360 --> 00:16:24,440
whether that's true or not.

180
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:26,200
Rin?

181
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:28,880
Phumin's daughter?

182
00:16:32,280 --> 00:16:34,760
Then where did you last see her?

183
00:16:37,280 --> 00:16:38,200
3C Corp.

184
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:41,880
Rin's been hunting Punlop

185
00:16:42,760 --> 00:16:44,120
because he killed her father.

186
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:46,600
Punlop.

187
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:48,640
You bastard!

188
00:16:58,320 --> 00:16:59,840
I've got an offer.

189
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:02,840
A very special one,

190
00:17:04,760 --> 00:17:05,640
just for you.

191
00:17:09,839 --> 00:17:11,760
What is it about this chair?

192
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:13,760
Whoever sits in it

193
00:17:14,480 --> 00:17:15,720
suddenly goes power-crazy.

194
00:17:19,119 --> 00:17:20,800
Where's Mrs. Giranun?

195
00:17:22,960 --> 00:17:24,800
On a long break.

196
00:17:25,920 --> 00:17:27,079
Liar.

197
00:17:30,760 --> 00:17:32,880
Right now,
there's a secret chat blowing up

198
00:17:34,080 --> 00:17:35,840
about a major media boss

199
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:37,480
breaking laws in multiple countries.

200
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:41,040
Don't threaten me.

201
00:17:42,040 --> 00:17:43,920
I found a file.

202
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:47,880
It says the media boss
secretly gave money to terrorists

203
00:17:47,960 --> 00:17:50,080
for inside access
to cover their operations.

204
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:51,760
But in reality,

205
00:17:53,600 --> 00:17:55,320
he was selling information
to the other side.

206
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:57,000
Shut up.

207
00:17:58,080 --> 00:17:59,480
My dad has nothing to do with this,

208
00:17:59,560 --> 00:18:00,920
and you have no proof.

209
00:18:02,080 --> 00:18:03,360
Then wait and see.

210
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:06,400
Worldwide breaking news.

211
00:18:07,760 --> 00:18:08,840
Should be out within the hour.

212
00:18:10,840 --> 00:18:11,720
You!

213
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:15,720
If you want me to stop this,

214
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:20,000
here's our deal.

215
00:18:22,080 --> 00:18:23,480
Stop helping Taiga.

216
00:18:24,760 --> 00:18:26,160
Don't get in my way.

217
00:18:26,760 --> 00:18:28,840
Don't make me come after you again.

218
00:18:30,560 --> 00:18:32,080
Stay out of it.

219
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:34,360
If you can't stay out of it,

220
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:36,480
get out of the country.

221
00:18:37,600 --> 00:18:39,760
You told me money is power.

222
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:41,960
Now I have both the money

223
00:18:42,040 --> 00:18:43,840
and the power to use.

224
00:18:44,480 --> 00:18:45,800
And this time, I mean it.

225
00:18:53,960 --> 00:18:56,360
This isn't a warning, Ratee.

226
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:21,480
Daddy.

227
00:19:22,480 --> 00:19:25,720
OUR COMPANY IS UNDER
GOVERNMENT INVESTIGATION

228
00:19:25,800 --> 00:19:29,040
DON'T COME BACK YET. TAKE CARE
I'LL CONTACT YOU ONCE I'M IN A SAFE PLACE

229
00:20:24,160 --> 00:20:25,360
Punlop!

230
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:27,560
I'm going to kill you!

231
00:20:27,640 --> 00:20:29,480
I'm going to kill you!

232
00:20:29,560 --> 00:20:30,720
It's a bit difficult.

233
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:36,040
But I'm doing exactly what you like.

234
00:20:36,120 --> 00:20:37,600
Lying,

235
00:20:37,680 --> 00:20:38,520
betraying,

236
00:20:38,600 --> 00:20:40,160
ambushing,

237
00:20:40,240 --> 00:20:41,240
backstabbing.

238
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:43,000
You tricked me!

239
00:20:43,600 --> 00:20:44,920
Consider it even.

240
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:47,800
You're Damon, and you never told me.

241
00:20:49,680 --> 00:20:51,640
How long were you going to use me?

242
00:20:52,960 --> 00:20:55,320
Until I died like a dog, serving you?

243
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:57,720
I told you before.

244
00:20:57,800 --> 00:20:59,520
I don't believe in love.

245
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:03,320
Love is for fools.

246
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:05,400
Good.

247
00:21:06,520 --> 00:21:08,160
Then I'll take it that you understand

248
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:10,360
if I punish you harshly.

249
00:21:13,040 --> 00:21:14,720
I misjudged you.

250
00:21:16,080 --> 00:21:17,720
I thought you were sincere

251
00:21:17,800 --> 00:21:19,560
and wanted me to replace Naruban.

252
00:21:20,840 --> 00:21:22,400
I judged you too kindly.

253
00:21:28,600 --> 00:21:30,200
You're going to sell the pathogen, right?

254
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:33,280
Not yet.

255
00:21:35,120 --> 00:21:36,800
I'll keep it

256
00:21:36,880 --> 00:21:38,800
for whoever bids highest.

257
00:21:40,280 --> 00:21:42,120
I'm not foolish enough to give it away

258
00:21:42,640 --> 00:21:44,920
just to feel good,
killing your children and husband.

259
00:21:45,680 --> 00:21:47,000
I've suffered enough.

260
00:21:48,160 --> 00:21:50,000
From now on, I live for myself.

261
00:21:52,240 --> 00:21:53,520
From now on,

262
00:21:54,040 --> 00:21:56,080
I'm the one who sets
the price for everything,

263
00:21:56,840 --> 00:21:58,640
decides everyone's survival.

264
00:22:03,880 --> 00:22:05,800
Rest and take some time for yourself.

265
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:09,640
Don't worry about your family.

266
00:22:10,160 --> 00:22:13,200
I'll take care of them, very well.

267
00:22:14,280 --> 00:22:15,360
Punlop!

268
00:22:15,440 --> 00:22:17,640
Let me go!

269
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:19,760
Punlop! Come back!

270
00:22:19,840 --> 00:22:21,080
Come back!

271
00:22:21,160 --> 00:22:23,880
I'll kill you!

272
00:22:23,960 --> 00:22:25,160
Come back!

273
00:22:25,240 --> 00:22:26,560
Come back!

274
00:23:07,080 --> 00:23:09,240
Looking so glum.

275
00:23:09,320 --> 00:23:10,440
Did someone scold you?

276
00:23:17,640 --> 00:23:19,440
I'm going back to France.

277
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:21,440
I miss home.

278
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:23,440
I miss Daddy.

279
00:23:25,400 --> 00:23:26,720
Are you okay, Ratee?

280
00:23:28,520 --> 00:23:30,360
Hey, wait.

281
00:23:35,240 --> 00:23:36,920
Why are you just leaving like this?

282
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:38,600
We haven't settled things here yet.

283
00:23:41,920 --> 00:23:42,760
Huh?

284
00:23:50,320 --> 00:23:51,720
What's wrong with her?

285
00:24:13,600 --> 00:24:14,960
Why are you crying?

286
00:24:15,040 --> 00:24:16,080
Mind your own business.

287
00:24:18,880 --> 00:24:19,920
Sit down.

288
00:24:21,360 --> 00:24:23,280
I've always meddled like this, haven't I?

289
00:24:25,320 --> 00:24:26,640
Just go.

290
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:29,280
Want me to come with you?

291
00:24:30,200 --> 00:24:31,880
Wherever you go,

292
00:24:31,960 --> 00:24:33,800
I'll go too.

293
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:34,840
I don't want you to be lonely.

294
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:39,160
I said go!

295
00:24:39,720 --> 00:24:42,440
Don't get involved. Don't ask.
Don't ask, understand?

296
00:24:42,520 --> 00:24:44,880
No need to push me away. It's pointless.

297
00:24:45,400 --> 00:24:46,800
No matter what,

298
00:24:46,880 --> 00:24:48,640
I'll always stay by your side.

299
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:54,160
No rush.

300
00:24:57,560 --> 00:24:58,680
Tell me when you're ready.

301
00:25:00,120 --> 00:25:01,320
I can wait.

302
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:02,240
Aru.

303
00:26:02,320 --> 00:26:03,720
Lee!

304
00:26:03,800 --> 00:26:05,120
How are you?

305
00:26:08,640 --> 00:26:10,560
How's Mr. Naruban?

306
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:13,080
Mr. Naruban is okay.

307
00:26:13,160 --> 00:26:15,720
But what about you? Are you okay?

308
00:26:16,280 --> 00:26:18,320
You don't sound well.

309
00:26:19,800 --> 00:26:21,240
I'm fine.

310
00:26:22,760 --> 00:26:25,160
Can you tell me where you are?

311
00:26:26,480 --> 00:26:28,600
If there's anything,
I'll contact you, Aru.

312
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:34,160
Lee.

313
00:27:10,440 --> 00:27:11,560
What's up, Aru?

314
00:27:18,480 --> 00:27:19,600
Thank you so much.

315
00:27:21,960 --> 00:27:23,040
Taiga!

316
00:27:23,120 --> 00:27:25,480
Taiga! Taiga!

317
00:28:28,920 --> 00:28:30,920
Dad, don't leave me.

318
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:34,640
Rin.

319
00:28:35,280 --> 00:28:36,240
Rin.

320
00:28:36,840 --> 00:28:37,880
It's okay.

321
00:28:40,080 --> 00:28:41,360
Aru told you.

322
00:28:43,240 --> 00:28:44,400
Don't blame Aru.

323
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:46,480
Everyone cares about you.

324
00:28:55,640 --> 00:28:57,680
I used to dream of my dad getting shot.

325
00:28:59,560 --> 00:29:01,160
I dreamed the car was sinking.

326
00:29:02,720 --> 00:29:04,960
My little brother trapped inside.
I'll never forget.

327
00:29:08,720 --> 00:29:11,560
It was the nightmare
of a child who lost his family.

328
00:29:13,400 --> 00:29:15,240
Memories of being lost,

329
00:29:17,320 --> 00:29:18,840
taken in and raised by others.

330
00:29:25,120 --> 00:29:26,800
I never got to see my brothers.

331
00:29:27,800 --> 00:29:29,400
I don't know if they're alive or dead.

332
00:29:41,320 --> 00:29:42,840
But the nightmare will end now.

333
00:29:50,400 --> 00:29:52,040
Taiga loves Rin so much.

334
00:29:53,360 --> 00:29:55,120
I can feel it.

335
00:29:55,640 --> 00:29:56,800
I see it.

336
00:29:59,720 --> 00:30:00,880
The truth hurts.

337
00:30:02,120 --> 00:30:03,280
But it doesn't last long.

338
00:30:05,280 --> 00:30:06,240
Yeah.

339
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:08,640
It hurts.

340
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:13,920
My life has things I need to do.

341
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:15,800
I should go back to my condo.

342
00:30:16,880 --> 00:30:17,720
Hey.

343
00:30:21,120 --> 00:30:23,160
Don't be alone. It's dangerous.

344
00:30:24,200 --> 00:30:26,320
What if Punlop goes crazy
and takes you again?

345
00:30:28,680 --> 00:30:29,520
I'll be fine.

346
00:30:32,360 --> 00:30:35,600
What can take Fire Phoenix down
from within,

347
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:38,000
besides what Inspector Phumin has?

348
00:30:49,320 --> 00:30:51,160
It has to be

349
00:30:52,640 --> 00:30:53,800
some crucial evidence.

350
00:30:56,360 --> 00:30:57,840
Hurry up and find it.

351
00:30:58,760 --> 00:31:01,520
If it were easy,
I'd have found it already.

352
00:31:01,600 --> 00:31:03,240
I wouldn't let it slide this long.

353
00:31:03,320 --> 00:31:04,640
Listen, Bear.

354
00:31:04,720 --> 00:31:07,160
I'm ordering you to act fast.
Start working.

355
00:31:11,320 --> 00:31:12,760
What's up with you?

356
00:31:18,880 --> 00:31:20,600
We'd need someone willing to testify,

357
00:31:21,240 --> 00:31:23,400
spill everything in court,

358
00:31:23,480 --> 00:31:25,720
which is rare.

359
00:31:27,720 --> 00:31:29,000
Who'd risk prison?

360
00:31:29,680 --> 00:31:32,520
Prisons aren't for rich people, madam.

361
00:31:34,520 --> 00:31:36,480
And you're just going
to give up that easily?

362
00:31:38,240 --> 00:31:39,280
Do it.

363
00:31:39,360 --> 00:31:41,520
If you want this world to be any better,

364
00:31:42,080 --> 00:31:43,640
you have to help Taiga.

365
00:31:44,440 --> 00:31:47,080
Justice will finally exist.

366
00:32:21,840 --> 00:32:23,440
Taiga told me you were here.

367
00:32:29,320 --> 00:32:31,080
Phumin told me once…

368
00:32:33,720 --> 00:32:35,000
that his youngest daughter

369
00:32:35,080 --> 00:32:36,520
was smart,

370
00:32:37,720 --> 00:32:39,000
athletic,

371
00:32:40,360 --> 00:32:41,880
and wanted to be a police officer.

372
00:32:50,600 --> 00:32:52,240
I need to apologize

373
00:32:53,440 --> 00:32:55,280
for misunderstanding you all this time.

374
00:33:08,440 --> 00:33:10,720
Taking down Fire Phoenix isn't easy.

375
00:33:11,960 --> 00:33:14,560
Officials, the rich,

376
00:33:15,160 --> 00:33:16,480
the powerful,

377
00:33:19,360 --> 00:33:22,240
they use justice for their own gain.

378
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:26,000
We have to destroy Fire Phoenix,

379
00:33:26,080 --> 00:33:28,000
even if it costs our lives.

380
00:33:37,880 --> 00:33:39,640
On that day, Dad would be so happy.

381
00:33:50,080 --> 00:33:52,760
There's nothing else for me to do, right?

382
00:33:52,840 --> 00:33:55,280
I'll take my leave and go home.

383
00:33:56,080 --> 00:33:58,320
You've worked as Naruban's secretary,

384
00:33:59,160 --> 00:34:00,320
Giranun's,

385
00:34:01,240 --> 00:34:03,080
and also helped me along the way.

386
00:34:09,400 --> 00:34:12,239
I think you deserve a special reward.

387
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:15,679
No, I don't want anything.

388
00:34:21,600 --> 00:34:23,600
I didn't see anything,
I don't know anything,

389
00:34:23,679 --> 00:34:25,840
and I'll never say a word
for the rest of my life.

390
00:34:28,600 --> 00:34:29,520
Very good.

391
00:34:40,920 --> 00:34:42,880
He must be seriously psychotic.

392
00:34:43,840 --> 00:34:46,120
Whoa.

393
00:34:46,199 --> 00:34:48,239
Please help me.

394
00:34:48,320 --> 00:34:50,239
I can't escape now.

395
00:34:56,639 --> 00:34:57,800
Dad.

396
00:34:58,520 --> 00:35:00,600
Atinuch sent a message.

397
00:35:02,640 --> 00:35:05,680
GIRANUN HAS BEEN HELD CAPTIVE BY PUNLOP

398
00:35:05,760 --> 00:35:07,400
Mom's been captured by Punlop.

399
00:35:10,600 --> 00:35:14,840
Right now, Punlop
is taking control of 3C Corp.

400
00:35:58,440 --> 00:35:59,320
Eat.

401
00:35:59,400 --> 00:36:00,880
Don't die too fast.

402
00:36:01,720 --> 00:36:03,920
I might still need to use you.

403
00:36:07,000 --> 00:36:08,800
I said eat!

404
00:36:40,240 --> 00:36:42,520
Why do you have to make me
get physical with you?

405
00:36:47,080 --> 00:36:50,080
No. I'm not cruel.

406
00:36:56,120 --> 00:36:57,520
Stay quiet.

407
00:36:58,680 --> 00:37:00,800
And see what I can do better than you

408
00:37:01,320 --> 00:37:02,960
as Damon.

409
00:37:39,960 --> 00:37:42,600
I know you don't want help from anyone.

410
00:37:45,040 --> 00:37:47,600
But let me do something for you.

411
00:37:54,040 --> 00:37:56,360
Let's make every minute count.

412
00:37:59,040 --> 00:38:00,880
We don't know what tomorrow will bring.

413
00:38:03,600 --> 00:38:04,600
Taiga.

414
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:07,880
Just being this kind to me is enough.

415
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:13,920
Can you believe it?

416
00:38:15,880 --> 00:38:17,960
I've never done this for anyone before.

417
00:38:27,840 --> 00:38:29,120
It's my fault

418
00:38:29,960 --> 00:38:31,680
for never daring to refuse anyone.

419
00:38:34,000 --> 00:38:36,760
I made the woman
I want to spend my life with hurt.

420
00:38:42,920 --> 00:38:44,920
Your walls are high.

421
00:38:48,560 --> 00:38:50,400
But I'll get past them, Rin.

422
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:36,280
I may be a stranger to everyone here.

423
00:39:37,240 --> 00:39:39,560
But Mrs. Giranun asked me to tell you.

424
00:39:39,640 --> 00:39:43,280
She's very stressed
about Mr. Naruban being sick.

425
00:39:44,080 --> 00:39:45,920
She's taking leave
to care for her husband.

426
00:39:48,440 --> 00:39:51,880
The new executive appointments
should be finalized by next week.

427
00:39:52,560 --> 00:39:55,240
Anyone not involved, get out of this room.

428
00:40:06,920 --> 00:40:08,520
Drag him out.

429
00:40:09,920 --> 00:40:10,800
Hey.

430
00:40:11,640 --> 00:40:13,320
We can settle this peacefully,
Mr. Naruban.

431
00:40:14,760 --> 00:40:17,000
Or do you want more bloodshed?

432
00:40:17,880 --> 00:40:18,920
Wait.

433
00:40:27,760 --> 00:40:29,560
Where did you take my mom?

434
00:40:31,320 --> 00:40:32,480
One hundred million,

435
00:40:33,320 --> 00:40:34,360
for your wife's life.

436
00:40:39,400 --> 00:40:40,480
Another hundred million,

437
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:42,800
to keep quiet about Fire Phoenix.

438
00:40:43,400 --> 00:40:45,040
Nobody's paying you that.

439
00:40:47,760 --> 00:40:49,080
Another hundred million,

440
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:50,880
for the pathogen.

441
00:40:51,920 --> 00:40:54,480
The one you ordered
to build a lab in this building.

442
00:40:55,080 --> 00:40:56,880
- You!
- Te!

443
00:40:56,960 --> 00:40:58,360
If you don't remember,

444
00:40:59,200 --> 00:41:00,600
I can play the clip on repeat.

445
00:41:10,200 --> 00:41:11,880
You're going to blackmail me with a clip.

446
00:41:12,720 --> 00:41:15,280
Do you think
I don't have evidence of your crimes?

447
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:17,600
You shot Inspector Phumin.

448
00:41:17,680 --> 00:41:19,480
If you have proof,

449
00:41:19,560 --> 00:41:20,840
let's go blow for blow.

450
00:41:22,320 --> 00:41:23,240
We'll see

451
00:41:23,320 --> 00:41:25,360
who gets destroyed more.

452
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:29,600
Between me, alone, one life,

453
00:41:30,680 --> 00:41:32,160
or 3C Corp.,

454
00:41:33,040 --> 00:41:34,480
with thousands of employees?

455
00:41:36,760 --> 00:41:38,400
You'll have everything seized,

456
00:41:39,200 --> 00:41:41,400
not a penny left
to buy even a bit of happiness.

457
00:41:53,600 --> 00:41:55,000
I'll pay you.

458
00:41:56,280 --> 00:41:57,880
Release Giranun.

459
00:41:58,400 --> 00:42:00,920
One payment, one installment.

460
00:42:04,480 --> 00:42:05,800
Then make it 500 million.

461
00:42:08,320 --> 00:42:10,840
Hesitate and your wife dies.

462
00:42:10,920 --> 00:42:13,280
You'll make headlines. Company closed,

463
00:42:13,360 --> 00:42:14,440
bankrupt,

464
00:42:14,520 --> 00:42:16,120
jailed.

465
00:42:20,960 --> 00:42:22,120
Want the scandalous clip

466
00:42:22,200 --> 00:42:23,880
all over social media?

467
00:42:26,160 --> 00:42:27,120
Go ahead, try it.

468
00:42:32,200 --> 00:42:34,160
- You bastard!
- Te!

469
00:42:53,000 --> 00:42:54,240
<i>We can't give him the money, Dad.</i>

470
00:42:55,080 --> 00:42:57,880
<i>A bastard like that, I know his nature.</i>

471
00:42:57,960 --> 00:42:59,720
<i>If we give him once,</i>

472
00:42:59,800 --> 00:43:01,520
<i>he'll blackmail us for life.</i>

473
00:43:01,600 --> 00:43:03,480
What about Mom, Te?

474
00:43:03,560 --> 00:43:05,120
Are we going to let her die?

475
00:43:11,880 --> 00:43:14,000
I have a secret account.

476
00:43:15,000 --> 00:43:16,680
The money's been moved overseas.

477
00:43:17,920 --> 00:43:19,360
It holds over 500 million.

478
00:43:26,040 --> 00:43:29,440
All the codes are on my flash drive.

479
00:43:36,320 --> 00:43:37,640
Someone's already taken it.

480
00:43:44,960 --> 00:43:46,800
Naruban's flash drive.

481
00:43:48,200 --> 00:43:49,600
From Naruban's office, sir.

482
00:43:50,280 --> 00:43:51,280
What's on it?

483
00:43:51,360 --> 00:43:52,680
I still can't open it.

484
00:43:52,760 --> 00:43:54,480
Take everything out of it.

485
00:43:55,080 --> 00:43:56,120
Yes, sir.

486
00:43:59,520 --> 00:44:02,640
So it was with you, Dhammatat.

487
00:44:11,400 --> 00:44:13,200
"Naruban's flash drive

488
00:44:13,800 --> 00:44:17,000
in exchange for incriminating files
about ratee's father."

489
00:44:22,680 --> 00:44:23,840
Punlop.

490
00:44:24,400 --> 00:44:25,360
You!

491
00:44:37,280 --> 00:44:38,720
Why can't I transfer it?

492
00:44:46,960 --> 00:44:48,040
My dear niece.

493
00:44:50,480 --> 00:44:52,520
You must die!

494
00:44:58,520 --> 00:45:00,640
Hey, Taiga!

495
00:45:30,960 --> 00:45:33,320
Subtitle translation by:
Chomchanach Yanaharn
